{"tid":1311462,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(live) 20190713 【逆權運動】一周一遊行 「光復上水」","createTime":"2019-07-13T07:57:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-13T09:16:39.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c8a308c759aa0e26eb93bea504d96b82820034b6","tid":1311462,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T07:57:52.000Z","msg":"(live) 20190713 【逆權運動】一周一遊行 「光復上水」<br />\n<br />\n【逆權運動】一周一遊行 「光復上水」<br />\n<br />\n由2012年開始，地區已發起多次「光復上水」行動，希望政府正視水貨客問題，但政府一直未有回應。曾經傳出受到鄉事派壓力的「光復上水」行動今日下午將如期舉行，行動將會於3時半在北區運動場籃球場出發，途經新發街、符興街、新功街，並以上水花園第一號作終點站。由「北區水貨客關注組」協助申請不反對通知書，預計有2,000人參與。由於途經地方均已迴避藥房重地新豐路，以及滿地拖篋的劍橋廣場停車場等水貨客重災區，故有網民呼籲遊行後前往「購物」。屆時《蘋果》將會直播。<br />\n<br />\n果燃台 live<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.feature.appledaily.com/goodestchannel/video/5d29515f9b6076000640085e/%E3%80%90%E9%80%86%E6%AC%8A%E9%81%8B%E5%8B%95%E3%80%91%E4%B8%80%E5%91%A8%E4%B8%80%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C%20%E3%80%8C%E5%85%89%E5%BE%A9%E4%B8%8A%E6%B0%B4%E3%80%8D?fromSource=App\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.feature.appledaily.com%2Fgoodestchannel%2Fvideo%2F5d29515f9b6076000640085e%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E9%2580%2586%25E6%25AC%258A%25E9%2581%258B%25E5%258B%2595%25E3%2580%2591%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%2591%25A8%25E4%25B8%2580%25E9%2581%258A%25E8%25A1%258C%2520%25E3%2580%258C%25E5%2585%2589%25E5%25BE%25A9%25E4%25B8%258A%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E3%2580%258D%3FfromSource%3DApp&d=ev%2BvVaAtQ3cORw7W3wlzWRSGsERVwMiaoyLN1PNQjS0%3D&h=7de68c45\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.feature.appledaily.com%2Fgoodestchannel%2Fvideo%2F5d29515f9b6076000640085e%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E9%2580%2586%25E6%25AC%258A%25E9%2581%258B%25E5%258B%2595%25E3%2580%2591%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%2591%25A8%25E4%25B8%2580%25E9%2581%258A%25E8%25A1%258C%2520%25E3%2580%258C%25E5%2585%2589%25E5%25BE%25A9%25E4%25B8%258A%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E3%2580%258D%3FfromSource%3DApp&h=af0974b3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.feature.appledaily.com/goodestchannel/video/5d29515f9b60